#: menus.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>saves the collection</action>. If the file is "
"<emphasis>Untitled</emphasis> then <guimenuitem>Save...</guimenuitem> is "
"equivalent to <guimenuitem>Save As</guimenuitem>. It is only enabled when "
"the collection has been modified."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>spašava kolekciju</action>. Ako je datoteka "
"<emphasis>Untitled</emphasis> onda <guimenuitem>Snimi...</guimenuitem>je  "
"ekvivalentno sa<guimenuitem>Snimi Kao</guimenuitem>. Dopušteno je samo kad "
"je kolekcija modifikovana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
