"Ova komanda <action>otvara dijalog okvir za preimenovanje  kolekcije</"
"action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Collection Fields...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Kolekcija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kolekcijska Polja...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Collection Fields Dialog</"
"interface></action>."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>otvara <interface>Dijalog Kolekcijskog Polja</"
"interface></action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generate Reports...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Kolekcija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generiši Izvještaj...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Report Dialog</interface></action> "
"for generating reports about the collection."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>otvara <interface>Dijalog Izvještaja</interface></"
"action> za generisanje izvještaja o kolekciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Convert to Bibliography</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Kolekcija</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pretvori u Bibliografiju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>converts a book collection to a bibliography</action> "
"by adding certain fields necessary for Bibtex export, and it is only enabled "
"when a book collection is open."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>pretvara kolekciju knjiga u bibliografiju</action> "
"dodavanjem određenih polja potrebnih za Bibtex eksport, i jedino je dopošten "
"kada je kolekcija knjiga otvorena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>String Macros...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Kolekcija</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>String Makroi...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens a dialog box for editing the Bibtex string "
"macros</action> in the collection. It is only enabled when editing a "
"bibliography."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>otvara dijalog okvir za izmjenu Bibtex string makroa</"
"action> u kolekciji. Dopušteno je jedino kad se vrši izmjena bibliografije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Check for Duplicate Keys</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Kolekcija</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Provjera Duplih Ključeva</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>checks for duplicate Bibtex keys</action> and can "
"filter the collection to show the entries with duplicated keys."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>provjerava da li ima duplih Bibtex ključeva</action> i "
"može filtrirati kolekciju da pokaže ulaze sa duplim ključevima."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Bibtex to Clipboard</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Kolekcija</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj Bibtex u Ostavu</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>copies a Bibtex citation</action> to the clipboard so "
"that it can pasted in a LaTeX document."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>kopira Bibtex citat</action>u ostavu da bi mogao biti "
"objavljen uLaTeX dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Cite Entry in Lyx</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Kolekcija</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Cite Entry in Lyx</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>sends a citation for the selected entries</action> to "
"the so-called <emphasis><link linkend=\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</"
"link></emphasis> for use in <application>LyX</application>, "
"<application>Kile</application>, or other LaTeX applications. It is only "
"enabled when editing a bibliography."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda <action>šalje citat za selektovani unos</action> u takozvani "
"<emphasis><link linkend=\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</link></"
"emphasis>za upotrebu u <application>LyX</application>, <application>Kile</"
"application>, ili drugim LaTeX aplikacijama.Dopušteno je jedino pri izmjeni "
"bibliografije."

